## Maintenance checklist

After finishing an implementation (or on a periodic review):

- [ ] Update feature checkboxes (`todo` / `partial` / `done`) for parents and children
- [ ] Set or clear `spec:` links; create `*.spec.md` when starting, not when inventing inbox ideas
- [ ] Add `Verified:` only after host smoke (Compose up, Tailscale reach, curl health / task)
- [ ] Move finished rows mentally into Done log if helpful
- [ ] Sync README / AGENTS roadmap sections only when **vision** changes (not every checkbox)
- [ ] New idea → Inbox first; do not invent alternate pipeline folders outside `.agents/specs/`

